{"tid":1565450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人人安居樂業 重會有人搞抗爭？","createTime":"2019-09-13T07:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T01:53:23.000Z","uid":122377,"like":20,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff6195a0cc11fcb60bc0ae095ec1fa59859b0c1","tid":1565450,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:04:33.000Z","msg":"講到尾香港既核心問題只有一個<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">地產霸權</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你可以話反送中條例係導火線 <br />\n但民生問題一定係樓價<br />\n<br />\n後生仔 買唔到樓 望唔到將來<br />\n無機會結婚生仔 成家立室 <br />\n如果要湊仔 邊有咁好精力同你上街 <br />\n<br />\n香港人人均收入唔低 但拎哂執去交租/供樓<br />\n到最後就比哂d錢 業主/地產商<br />\n<br />\n尋日新地出業績 又賺幾百億 <br />\n如果經濟唔好個期 政府一年盈餘都未必夠佢多<br />\n咁你可以見到個問題有幾嚴重"},{"pid":"6a6ef8cbd9834b0d8dad2141d50ec943603b9c77","tid":1565450,"uid":318637,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89944fb43ad7634c406c6d593fe011dbafedbb3e","tid":1565450,"uid":255816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"【行動po】全民文宣日！每星期一齊貼連儂貼文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565381</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思借個位宣傳<br />\n小妹提議每星期一四晚做全民文宣<br />\n一齊出街貼連儂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc72c1adb6f64e4e385bfbf3deb8e97c4b2c3777","tid":1565450,"uid":122377,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"好心你地槍頭對準地產商啦 <br />\n樓價下跌 一定個個人都開心左 幸福左"},{"pid":"3f614d27933dfe5b00278b5431e4dc861ab1156a","tid":1565450,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" 