mg src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n呢d錯誤谷大左房屋既需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，先係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問題根源</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"每日150支那狗係其中一個因素，但唔係主要囉，個150人大多數都係排公屋，正常香港人，一個都搵20-30k，點排啊<br />\n洗黑錢個啲支那狗就炒貴啲豪宅"},{"pid":"d344584ccbf2221e57a6434c027d26af70a99f0b","tid":1565450,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"19e21ac5adc119822067987e802a83b283a73365","tid":1565450,"uid":77170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對準問題根源<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">每日150人，輸入所謂既磚材<br />\n有錢落黎黑錢變白錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，窮L落黎佔用社會資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n呢d錯誤谷大左房屋既需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，先係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問題根源</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:31:37.000Z","msg":"呢個問題又係老生常談<br />\n無150輸入 香港無哂清潔工 譚仔阿姐 <br />\n香港人重點會生活得舒服？<br />\n<br />\n輸入150係無錯既 人地夫妻有需要團聚 <br />\n香港亦需要廉價而年輕既勞力 <br />\n試問香港本地人 點會做洗碗 洗廁所 譚仔阿姐？<br />\n唔好人講150唔好 你又話唔好 <br />\n<br />\n咁有人呃綜援 香港大把的士佬都呃 又逃稅啦 <br />\n政府無為150個 做好房屋措施又係真既 所以要屌 <br />\n但次次政府出黎要起野 你地同地產商又反對反對<br />\n當年8萬5 又50萬人上街 <br />\n咁你地想政府點發展？"},{"pid":"0bef3baed5ef995ee98037b5576bf64a2a341cc0","tid":1565450,"uid":61914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:32:09.000Z","msg":"Blocked<br />\nOn9"},{"pid":"539fe617b084531a9fcf5e1d50c4897f545e1ed9","tid":1565450,"uid":213489,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c30f8a41f43ca21047548897d9396600bf73c0e","tid":1565450,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:30:18.000Z","msg":"又block一件"},"